# ─── local SQLite database ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# The DB holds every per-turn token count, session ID, project path, and
# message UUID parsed out of ~/.claude/projects/*/*.jsonl — i.e. your full
# private usage history. NEVER commit.
data/*.db
data/*.db-shm
data/*.db-wal

# Backfill stampede lockfile — mtime-based, regenerated on demand.
data/.backfill.lock

# ─── python caches ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/

# ─── personal scratch / local state ────────────────────────────────────
# next_steps.md is a personal nightly-generated TODO log — keep local.
next_steps.md

# Claude Code project-local settings (per-user allowlist / hooks).
.claude/

# ─── editor / OS cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── build / dist ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
build/
dist/
*.egg
